    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎩🍻 <strong>Beer and Rush: Non-Vr Edition</strong> is a short game inspired by a real-life experience: after a few beers, I dreamed of desperately searching for a bathroom. Beer barrels chased me, I kept falling, and my friends couldn't stop laughing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Check out the non-VR version of the original 'Beer and Rush VR,' also on Steam!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strap in for a pee-rific adventure:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🌌🚽 Get lost in the dreams as you search for the relief station—a.k.a. the bathroom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🕯️🎸 Light up the night with <strong>lanterns</strong> in your virtual hands.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🎶🌙 Jump through a moonlit level accompanied by Clair de Lune.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎵🍺 And yes, you'll actually hear Clair de Lune and Gymnopédies as you make that &quot;one small <strong>leap</strong> for man, but a <strong>giant sip</strong> for mankind.&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🎩🎶Enjoy our <strong>original soundtrack </strong>  featuring rock and funk.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a surreal, beer-induced adventure that blurs the boundaries of dreams and reality!!! 🎵🍻</p>",
